title: Looking Back At SEC & ACC Media Days
description:
Christine Williamson, Harry Lyles Jr. and Tom Luginbill tell us everything you need to know about a busy week for the SEC and ACC. While Jimbo Fisher clears the air on his "feud" with Nick Saban, while Miami moves on from their signature turnover chain.
